Introduction

Elisia is a Filipino singer and actress under F&F Entertainment. In 2023, Elisia participated in the SBS survival show "Universe Ticket" where she finished 1st place, securing her spot as a member of the South Korean project girl group UNIS.

Elisia debuted as a member of UNIS on March 27, 2024, with their first mini-album "WE UNIS" and the title track "SUPERWOMAN."
